### Create Address for Customer
POST http://localhost:5001/api/v1/addresses
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "customerId": "50682m68-9c02-4a6b-97a2-33010792b7e6",
  "receiverName": "Nguyen Van A",
  "receiverPhone": "0909123456",
  "addressLine": "123 Nguyen Hue, District 1, Ho Chi Minh City",
  "label": "Home",
  "isDefault": true
}

### Create Address for Store
POST http://localhost:5001/api/v1/addresses
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "storeId": "fd102949-677b-4843-ada1-8a940c738438",
  "addressLine": "456 Le Loi, District 1, Ho Chi Minh City",
  "label": "Warehouse"
}

### Update Address
PUT http://localhost:5001/api/v1/addresses/address-uuid-here
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "receiverName": "Nguyen Van B",
  "addressLine": "789 Pastuer, District 3, Ho Chi Minh City"
}

### Set Default Address
PATCH http://localhost:5001/api/v1/addresses/address-uuid-here/default
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### List Addresses by Customer
GET http://localhost:5001/api/v1/addresses/customer/50682m68-9c02-4a6b-97a2-33010792b7e6
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### List Addresses by Store
GET http://localhost:5001/api/v1/addresses/store/fd102949-677b-4843-ada1-8a940c738438
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Delete Address
DELETE http://localhost:5001/api/v1/addresses/address-uuid-here
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
